    "body": "I think this is a somewhat general issue with `&mut` iterators. `Peakable` iterators also suffer from this.\n\n``` rust\nfn main() {\n    let a = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5];\n    let mut it = a.iter();\n    {\n        let mut it2 = it.by_ref().peekable();\n        let _ = it2.peek();\n    }\n    for i in it {\n        println!(\"{}\", i);\n    }\n}\n```\n",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
